here are texts of letters between 
ayatollah ali montazeri and ayatollah ruhollah khomeini indicating 
that montazeri is being ousted as khomeinis successor they were 
translated from tehran radio reports monitored by the associated 
press 
montazeris letter to khomeini 
i received your letter dated march 26 
i thank you for your kindness and guidance and assure you that 
just as i have been like an obedient soldier always with you in the 
way of islam and the revolution now too i see myself compelled to 
obey your orders because the survival and stability of the islamic 
republic rests on obeying your orders 
it is not doubtful for anyone that this great islamic revolution 
has passed through many dangers through your leadership and 
guidance and has thwarted many enemies such as the heartless 
monafeqin hypocrites referring to iranian rebels whose hands 
are red with the blood of thousands of our people and our great 
personalities including my own son and many other opposing 
fronts and antirevolutionaries and misled liberals 
can anyone forget the horrific crimes and the inhumane blows of 
these heartless lot to the revolution and the nation 
and if their mouthpieces and alien radios think that by 
spreading rumors about me they can reach their vile goals and 
cause rifts in the unity of our nation they are greatly mistaken 
and about my designation as your successor 
i myself was seriously opposed to it and with attention to the 
many difficulties and the heaviness of the burden of 
responsibility wrote to the council of experts at the time that my 
designation was not correct and now i openly declare my lack of 
readiness and ask you to order the council of experts to keep in 
mind the good of the future of islam the revolution and the 
nation and allow me just like before to remain a small teacher in 
the islamic schools under your guidance 
and if there have been mistakes which are the nature of 
mankind god willing they will be rectified by your guidance 
and i would like to ask my dear brothers and sisters not to do 
anything about the the great leaders decision anb the council of 
experts using their support for me as an excuse 
because the leader and the council want nothing but the good of 
the nation 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
khomeinis letter accepting montazeris resignation 
as you have written the leadership of the islamic republic is a 
difficult task it is a very grave responsibility which requires 
endurance more than your capacity 
for that reason both you and i were both from the beginning 
against your appointment in this regard both thought in the same 
way 
but the experts council of experts had arrived at that 
conclusion and i did not want to interfere in their legal 
jurisdiction 
having accepted your resignation i sincerely thank you for 
declaring your lack of readiness for the position of deputy 
leadership everybody knows that you are the result of my life as 
a student and that i have strong attachment to you 
in order that former mistakes are not repeated i advise you to 
cleanse your household from unsuitable individuals and seriously 
prevent the comings and goings of the opponents of the system who 
pretend to be in favor of islam and the islamic republic 
i also gave you the same advice in the case of mehdi hashemi 
i see your interests and that of the revolution in the fact that 
you must be a theologian whose views could be utilized by the 
regime and the people 
do not be affected by the spread of lies from foreign radio 
stations our people know you well they have also learned well of 
tricks by the enemy who show their enmity to islam by making 
false attributions to iranian authorities 
the dear scholars and the leaders of the friday prayers as 
well as the media should clafify this simple matter for the 
people that in islam the good of the regime takes precedence over 
everything else and we must all obey this 
</TEXT>
