enforce an interstate agreement requiring states to extradite 
juveniles charged with crimes by other states 
failing to honor that agreement alper argued would quickly 
turn the nations capital into a haven for fleeing fugitives 
eilperin said he would rule thursday morning on alabamas 
petition to extradite the youth identified only by the initials 
om he also said he would issue an immediate stay of that ruling 
